Pretty much a harder version of your schedule. EE120 harder but less work than ee16b, cs170 much harder than 70, around same work, 61C easier but more work than 61B. CS188 is one of the easiest CS classes here, probably easier than ee16b

-------------------

In my experience, your current schedule is much easier than your proposed schedule. 170 is easier than 70 and less work, 120 is easier than 16b and has less work. If you're able to manage your time with that schedule, you should be more than fine with your new one. 188 in my experience is even easier than 120, although it will be more work.
